1.name: Maximum
1.description: Cubelet will modify the block values it receives. When multiple inputs are received, it will share only the largest of the block values.

1.name: Minimum
1.description: Cubelet will modify the block values it receives. When multiple inputs are received, it will share only the smallest of the block values.

1.name: Passive
